Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.27,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.18,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:53.69,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
